asWright" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/JonasWright">Jonas Wright</a> (1642)</li><li> "<a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/IntoTheSun" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/IntoTheSun">Into the Sun</a>" by <a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/RobertDuncanMilne" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/RobertDuncanMilne">Robert Duncan Milne</a> (1882)</li><li> "<a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/ExtractFromCaptainStormfieldsVisitToHeaven" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/ExtractFromCaptainStormfieldsVisitToHeaven">Captain Stormfield's Visit to Heaven</a>" by <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/MarkTwain" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/MarkTwain">Mark Twain</a> (1907)</li><li> "<a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TheCometDoom" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TheCometDoom">The Comet Doom</a>" by <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/EdmondHamilton" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/EdmondHamilton">Edmond Hamilton</a> (1928)</li><li> "<a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/Sunspot" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/Sunspot">Sunspot</a>" by <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/HalClement" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/HalClement">Hal Clement</a> (1960)</li><li> "<a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/IntoTheComet" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/IntoTheComet">Inside the Comet</a>" by Arthur C. Clarke (1960)</li><li> "<a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/Raindrop" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/Raindrop">Raindrop</a>" by Hal Clement (1960)</li><li> "<a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/CometWine" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/CometWine">Comet Wine</a>" by <a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/RayRussell" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/RayRussell">Ray Russell</a> (1967)</li><li> "<a class="createlink" href="/