i><li> "<a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/SoldierBoy" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/SoldierBoy">Soldier Boy</a>" by Michael Shaara (1953)</li><li> "<a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/FarewellToTheMaster" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/FarewellToTheMaster">Farewell to the Master</a>" by <a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/HarryBates" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/HarryBates">Harry Bates</a> (1940)</li></ul><hr><hr><h2>Works collected in #10 <em>Invasions</em> (1990):</h2><ul><li> "<a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/LivingSpace" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/LivingSpace">Living Space</a>" by Isaac Asimov (1956)</li><li> "<a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/Asylum" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/Asylum">Asylum</a>" by A.E. van Vogt (1942)</li><li> "<a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/Exposure" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/Exposure">Exposure</a>" by Eric Frank Russell (1950)</li><li> "<a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/InvasionOfPrivacy" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/InvasionOfPrivacy">Invasion of Privacy</a>" by Bob Shaw (1970)</li><li> "<a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/WhatHaveIDone" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/WhatHaveIDone">What Have I Done?</a>" by <a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/MarkClifton" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/MarkClifton">Mark Clifton</a> (1952)</li><li> "<a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/Impostor" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/Impostor">Impostor</a>" by Philip K. Dick (1953)</li><li> "<a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TheSoulEmptyOnes" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TheSoulEmptyOnes">The Soul-Empty Ones</a>" by <a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/WalterMMillerJr" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/WalterMMillerJr">Wal